                                <date>1958</date>. С. <biblScope unit="page">??–??</biblScope>.</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><encodingDesc><tagsDecl>&amp;renditions;</tagsDecl></encodingDesc></teiHeader><text><body><entry xml:id="entry_ǧæwaj" xml:lang="os-x-digor"><form type="lemma"><orth>ǧæwaj</orth></form><usg><lang/></usg><re><form type="lemma"><orth>ǧæwaj kænun </orth></form><sense><sense><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>стеречь</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>guard</q></tr></sense><sense><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>охранять</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>protect</q></tr></sense></sense></re><etym xml:lang="ru">Восходит к <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><lang/> <w>*gavāya-</w> <gloss><q>кричать</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="ira"><w/> <gloss><q>давать знать криками (об опасности и пр.)</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><w/> <gloss><q>призывать (на помощь)</q></gloss></mentioned>, ; ср. <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><lang/> <w>gu-, gaw-</w> <gloss><q>звучать</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/> <gloss><q>кричать</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w>joguve</w> <gloss><q>громко кричу</q></gloss></mentioned>, , <mentioned xml:lang="ru"><lang/> <w>говор, говорить</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="grc"><lang/> <w>γοάω</w> <gloss><q>воплю</q></gloss></mentioned>; или (из и.е. *%iġh%i-) <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><lang/> <w>havate</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/> <w>zavaiti</w> <gloss><q>призывает</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ru"><lang/> <w>зову, звать</w></mentioned>. Иронское %iqakkænyn%i нет оснований отделять от %iǧæwaj kænun%i (→ *%iqwaj kænyn%i → %iqakkænyn%i); ср. д. %igæwaǵǵin%i → и. %iqaǵǵyn%i.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">It traces back to <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><lang/> <w>*gavāya-</w> <gloss><q>shout</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="ira"><w/> <gloss><q>let know (about danger etc.) by shouting</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><w/> <gloss><q>to call (for help)</q></gloss></mentioned>, ; ср. <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><lang/> <w>gu-, gaw-</w> <gloss><q>sound</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/> <gloss><q>shout</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w>joguve</w> <gloss><q>I am shouting loudly</q></gloss></mentioned>, , <mentioned xml:lang="ru"><lang/> <w>говор</w> <gloss><q>dialect</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="ru"><w>говорить</w> <gloss><q>speak</q></gloss></mentioned>, , <mentioned xml:lang="grc"><lang/> <w>γοάω</w> <gloss><q>I am screaming</q></gloss></mentioned>; or (from I.E. *%iġh%i-) <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><lang/> <w>havate</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/> <w>zavaiti</w> <gloss><q>he summons</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ru"><lang/> <w>зову</w> <gloss><q>I call</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="ru"><w>звать</w> <gloss><q>call</q></gloss></mentioned>, . There are no grounds to separate Iron %iqakkænyn%i from %iǧæwaj kænun%i (→ *%iqwaj kænyn%i → %iqakkænyn%i); cf. Digor %igæwaǵǵin%i → Iron %iqaǵǵyn%i.</etym></entry></body></text></TEI>